==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ampliative
<hw>Am"pli*a*tive</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Logic)</fld>
<def>Enlarging a conception by adding to that which is already known or
received.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>⟦ldquo⟧All bodies possess power of attraction⟦rdquo⟧ is an
<qex>ampliative</qex> judgment; because we can think of bodies without
thinking of attraction as one of their immediate primary attributes.</q>
<rj><qau>Abp. W. Thomson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amplificate</ent>⟦br⟧
